OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear night to come with perhaps a few
OL,7,Fmist and fog patches forming. A chilly
OL,8,Fnight with perhaps a touch of frost in
OL,9,Fthe countryside.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAnother dry, sunny and fine
OL,12,Fday on Tuesday, although skies may
OL,13,Fturn hazy across the far west later.
OL,14,FFeeling warm, especially in the
OL,15,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
