OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying dry, sunny and warm on
OL,7,FWednesday. Turning cooler and
OL,8,Fchangeable on Thursday with bands of
OL,9,Frain and showers moving across the
OL,10,Fregion. Perhaps turning wet and windy
OL,11,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
